        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Once your university applications have been submitted, the waiting period can be filled with uncertainty. Grant Consulting takes the guesswork out of this stage by actively monitoring the status of every application you have submitted. We keep you informed with regular updates so you always know exactly where things stand — whether an application is under review, requires additional documents, or has received a decision.</p>
          <p>Managing deadlines across multiple universities and countries is a challenge that catches many students off guard. Our team maintains a comprehensive tracking system that monitors not just application deadlines but also scholarship submission dates, enrollment confirmation windows, housing deposit due dates, and visa appointment timelines. We send proactive reminders well in advance so you never miss a critical date.</p>
          <p>When universities need additional information or documents, we handle the follow-up communication on your behalf. Whether it is responding to an admissions office inquiry, submitting updated test scores, or requesting a status update on a delayed decision, our team acts as your point of contact to keep the process moving forward. This hands-on approach saves you time and ensures that no request goes unanswered.</p>
        </div>

